metadata.name: #OnlyCans NFT PlaceHolder
metadata.description: Every Only Can NFT is unique. Each piece of art is autogenerated from over 800+ features which have been dedicatedly hand-drawn by our artist Anastasia Shishneva. Each Can exists as an ERC-721 token on the Ethereum Blockchain, and is hosted on IPFS, With an initial Mint cost of 0.04 ETH Hodling a Can grants you copyright and commercial usage, as well as access to future airdrops, and exclusive early access to features like The OCACS and the OCA.
